<p>A romance! Kaia Gerber and Jacob Elordi have been seen out in New York City several times this week sparking rumours of a blossoming romance. And on Wednesday evening the 19-year-old supermodel and the 23-year-old Kissing Booth actor proved they are indeed an item</p>

<p>Close as can be: The two have not yet shown affection, but on this night out they seemed find as they held hands while walking past onlookers</p>

<p>The pair seemed to be very into each other as they could not keep far apart during the stroll through the city.</p>

<p>They were in step as they held hands then at one point the Australian actor put his arms around the daughter of Cindy Crawford and Rande Gerber.</p>

<p>Kaia looked on-trend with a large black leather blazer with a wife lapel, broad shoulders and pockets on the sides.</p>

<p>Another PDA: And at one point the handsome movie star put his arm around his new lady love</p>

<p>She let him know she liked his affection: And here the model is seen holding onto his hand as her other arm went around his waist</p>

<p>Underneath was a black tube top that exposed her trim tummy.</p>

<p>And she added high-waisted jeans that came to her ankle, showing off her military boots in black.</p>

<p>The catwalk expert had a light brown purse on her shoulder and was in a surgical face mask.</p>

<p>They have the same vibe: Not only were they both in step, but they had on matching jeans</p>

<p>Her hair was parted in the middle with the pink tips still in place as she had on light makeup and delicate gold earrings.</p>

<p>Jacob looked like a fashionista in the making as he tucked his black and floral Hawaiian shirt into his belted, high-waisted jeans.</p>

<p>The budding star added lace-up workman boots in dark brown. And he seemed to have a gold chain necklace as well as a gold bracelet and gold rings.</p>

<p>They can't keep their hands off each other! In this image, Elordi has both hands on the teen</p>

<p>Earlier in the day they were seen on another walk but there was no PDA. </p>

<p>Jacob's hand lingered on Kaia's arm as the duo walked out of the gym together.  The duo didn't exactly try and keep their distance at various points of the walk.  </p>

<p>Kaia led the way in a dark blue sports bra, leggings, and white trainers, while Jacob followed close behind in shorts and a T-shirt.</p>

<p>The duo both wore matching blue medical masks and sunglasses.</p>

<p>Dinner for two! Kaia pulled down her mask as she held on to her beverage as Jacob looked on</p>

<p>Kaia slicked her pink-tint tresses back, the perfect hairdo for a trip to the gym. </p>

<p>The pair have 13 Reasons Why actor Tommy Dorfman as a mutual friend, whom they have both been spending time with during lockdown.</p>

<p>Celebrity Instagram account deuxmoi, which posts texts and DMs from followers about celebrity encounters, shared several stories about the rumored couple in New York City.  </p>

<p>Is love on the menu? The screen idol looked intrigued as he stared at the cover girl</p>

<p>The two were seen out in the city by various people, with one follower submitting a photo of the couple holding hands.</p>

<p>The lookers were then seen hanging out Washington Square Park, followed by dinner at Bar Pitti.</p>

<p>'I just saw Jacob Elordi and Kaia Gerber on a date in nyc and the beauty those two hold' a fan tweeted.</p>

<p>While sources say Kaia and Jacob are romantically interested in one another, it is the model who isn't ready to commit due to her rising career, according to E!</p>

<p>'Kaia is the one that doesn't want to be in an exclusive relationship right now. She has a lot of projects on her plate and wants her freedom,' a source said.</p>

<p>'She does love hanging out with Jacob and they are spending time in New York City for the week while she works.'</p>

<p>Jacob has been linked to his former Euphoria co-star Zendaya and Joey King, whom he starred with in The Kissing Booth. </p>

<p>Romantic past: Jacob has been linked to his former Euphoria co-star Zendaya and Joey King, whom he starred with in The Kissing Booth (pictured with Zendaya in 2019)</p>

