<p>While the two never announced their relationship, a source confirmed the actors were indeed dating in an Us Weekly report in February 2020. </p>

<p>Jacob's recent outings with Kaia have sparked speculation his relationship with Zendaya has ended.  </p>

<p>Kaia was previously in a relationship with SNL star Pete Davidson, but recently landed at the center dating rumors with fellow model Cara Delevingne when the duo were spotted affectionately embracing at a Black Lives Matter rally in July.</p>

<p>Not only that, but the women also got matching 'Solemate' tattoos on their feet in August. </p>

